question: Who won the Nobel Prize in Physics in 2020?
gold_query: MATCH (s:Scholar)-[:WON]->(p:Prize {awardYear: 2020, category: "physics"}) RETURN s.knownName
rag_query: MATCH (s:Scholar)-[:WON]->(p:Prize {awardYear: 2020, category: "physics"}) RETURN s.knownName
initial_query: MATCH (s1:Scholar)-[r1:WON]->(p1:Prize) WHERE p1.category = 'Physics' AND p1.awardYear = 2020 RETURN s1.fullName

question: Which laureates won more than one Nobel Prize?
gold_query: MATCH (s:Scholar)-[:WON]->(p:Prize) WITH s, COUNT(p) as prizes WHERE prizes > 1 RETURN s.knownName
rag_query: MATCH (s:Scholar)-[:WON]->(p:Prize) WITH s, COUNT(p) AS numPrizes WHERE numPrizes > 1 RETURN s.knownName
initial_query: MATCH (s1:Scholar)-[r1:WON]->(p1:Prize) WITH s1, count(p1) AS numPrizes WHERE numPrizes > 1 RETURN s1.id
gold_result: [('John Bardeen',), ('Linus Pauling',), ('Frederick Sanger',), ('K. Barry Sharpless',), ('Marie Curie',)]

rag_query: MATCH (s:Scholar)-[:WON]->(p:Prize) WHERE lower(s.knownName) CONTAINS lower('Curie') AND lower(s.knownName) CONTAINS lower('Marie') RETURN p.category

question: Who won the Nobel Prize in peace in 1962?
gold_query: MATCH (s:Scholar)-[:WON]->(p:Prize {awardYear: 1962, category: "peace"}) RETURN s.knownName

initial_query: MATCH (s:Scholar)-[w:WON]->(p:Prize) WHERE p.awardYear = 1962 AND toLower(p.category) CONTAINS 'peace' RETURN s.fullName

question: List all Nobel Peace Prize winners.
gold_query: MATCH (s:Scholar)-[:WON]->(p:Prize {category: "peace"}) RETURN DISTINCT s.knownName

question: How many laureates are female?
